{"tid":1550732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣佈：所有阻止私了既左膠都係對家臥底，可以私了埋一份","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T20:29:31.000Z","uid":57308,"like":45,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ce193aba69b8f4bf46dfef27d4a77bc61de9da1c","tid":1550732,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b4f34ea91ee080bd3db74d619a19a5da2aa9e8","tid":1550732,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:22:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cb853a2ca7b1339c021a32f0a348e53f7d8af69","tid":1550732,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b0e0245945fd2ffecb11e53bbbf8553e37d9793","tid":1550732,"uid":57308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:23:36.000Z","msg":"阻止打藍屍廢老既一律打埋一份"},{"pid":"015a11120911a59cee3e11f1433165769d0d7f8b","tid":1550732,"uid":57308,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTi